Chris Rush https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Rush 0 Chris Rush is an American comedian, writer, actor, radio personality and author. He is best known for his stand-up routines and albums, along with having been a writer and editor on the satirical publication National Lampoon magazine.
